channel.title: Goblin killa
channel.description: well i just want to have a simple script to walk behind lumbridge castle, kill goblins, pickup bones, bury bones, and walk back if it died. one that uses SRL with anti-ban and anti-randoms and all that crap. this doesn't need any fancy walking procedures, just align to north and do constant + random(4) pixels [x, not y] and a 3-5 second wait between every click(with a random variation)
